data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a vibrant community! This 3-bedroom, 2-bath, 2-car garage ranch-style gem is a showstopper! Step inside and you'll be greeted by high ceilings that give this home an airy and open feel. The cleverly designed split bedroom floor plan ensures privacy and convenience for all family members. Picture yourself hosting memorable gatherings in the spacious living room dining room combo, perfect for entertaining friends and family. Speaking of entertaining, just wait until you step onto the enclosed screen porch, which was recently installed in January 2023 and spans the entire length of the home - it's the ideal spot for sipping morning coffee or enjoying evening sunsets overlooking the beautifully maintained landscaped yard.  But that's not all - this fantastic home is just a short 6-mile drive to the beach, making those sunny weekend getaways a breeze! Need a little outdoor inspiration? You'll love the versatile outside work space area, which can easily be converted into your own BBQ oasis, perfect for grilling up a storm on warm summer evenings. With a brand-new roof, expansive enclosed screen porch, and a newly installed enclosed wooden fence in January 2023, this home is ready for you to move right in and start making lasting memories.   Plus, rest easy knowing this beauty is not in a flood zone. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this house your forever home!
